OL,3,CThe homeless people hoping for change
OL,4,Cafter election day
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports on whether the
OL,7,Felection could change the region's
OL,8,Fhomelessness crisis
OL,10,FPeople who are homeless in Devon and
OL,11,FCornwall are calling on the next
OL,12,Fgovernment to build more houses and
OL,13,Fprovide more support the most
OL,14,Fvulnerable in society.
OL,16,FWith less than a week to go until
OL,17,Fpolling day, ITV News West Country has
OL,18,Fspoken to people sleeping rough or
OL,19,Fbeing helped by charities in Newquay
OL,20,Fand Exeter.
