OL,3,CThe homeless people hoping for change
OL,4,Cafter election day
OL,6,FThey say they hope a new Parliament
OL,7,Fwill bring about 'much-needed' changes.
OL,9,FJeanette Garside, originally from
OL,10,FManchester, has been living in a small
OL,11,Fhotel room in Newquay for the past
OL,12,Fseven months after a family dispute.
OL,14,F"It has affected me a lot," she said.
OL,16,F"I've lost a lot of weight. I was nine
OL,17,Fstone, I'm now just under six. I was
OL,18,Fin hospital a couple of weeks ago, I
OL,19,Fhad an ulcer on my chin."
