OL,3,CThe homeless people hoping for change
OL,4,Cafter election day
OL,6,F"I just feel like I've been pushed
OL,7,Ffrom pillar to post and I'm getting no
OL,8,Fhelp," she said.
OL,10,FMonique Collins, who runs the Drop In
OL,11,FAnd Share (DISC) charity in Newquay,
OL,12,Fsaid: "They are all promising to build
OL,13,Faffordable social housing, and I do
OL,14,Fhope the party that comes into power
OL,15,Fwill make that promise come true
OL,16,Fbecause we desperately need it.
OL,18,F"We've got so many people who are
OL,19,Fhomeless on the streets or stuck in
OL,20,Fhotel rooms, and it's unacceptable."
