OL,3,CThe homeless people hoping for change
OL,4,Cafter election day
OL,6,FThe housing charity, St Petrock's, has
OL,7,Fpublished its own manifesto, setting
OL,8,Fout what it would like to see from a
OL,9,Fnew government.
OL,11,FDirector Peter Stephenson said:
OL,12,F"Homelessness is far more than a lack
OL,13,Fof roofs, important though that is.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
