OL,3,CThe homeless people hoping for change
OL,4,Cafter election day
OL,6,F"What government seems to be very very
OL,7,Fpoor at is understanding that
OL,8,Fvulnerable people, without support,
OL,9,Feven if they have access to a roof,
OL,10,Fwon't be able to hold it together,
OL,11,Fwon't be able to budget, won't be able
OL,12,Fto keep to the terms of their tenancy
OL,13,Fagreement, won't be able to deal with
OL,14,Ffacing eviction, to be able to
OL,15,Fnegotiate a way out with their
OL,16,Flandlord.
OL,18,F"We need much more investment in
OL,19,Fsupport services to stop people
OL,20,Fbecoming homeless in the first place",
OL,21,Fhe added.
